"...Damn it! Damn it, Damn it, DAMN IT!": "What- what the- what WAS that! I never knew that thing existed!"
"I've been completely obliterated! I, Hagith Anie! I, one of the chosen!"
"I can't face \"Mother\" like this... It'll affect my company!"
"No, not yet! I haven't lost yet!"
"My army is indestructible! Isn't that right... Emerald Tablet!"

"...Now, take it, take in the Ether! Emerald Tablet!"

"Show me power beyond anything money can buy, Emerald Tablet! Your constructions... have no limits!"
